data.description: Mid-century ranch in very desirable southside location with many updates! This home has a unique layout on the main level which has been updated with beautiful wood look flooring. Large windows in your living room overlook your own private covered patio area. This room also has the original stone feature wall that mid-century fans will love. The primary bedroom is large and has siding doors out to your deck. The basement is almost complete, ready for your finishing touches, with a huge family room space and an additional half bath. Stay dry year round with your connected carport, just two walls short of being a full garage. The backyard is fully fenced for your kids and pets, with a huge storage shed for all your lawn gear. Newer roof, A/C, water heater, and windows as well! Don't miss this one! Schedule your showing today!
